  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Source, Typed

    public class ConstValue
extends SimpleValue
    A special SimpleValue of type integer, that holds a predefined constant. In addition to the numerical value stored as SimpleValue, the representation of the underlying value as a Enigma API constant is saved as a, instance of Constants.
